title: Sally Hansen Insta, Dri Insta, Dri Anti, Chip Top Coat
description: Sally Hansen insta-dri anti-chip top coat is a quick, dry, chip resistant top coat. Dries any nail color. 30 seconds to set. No-chip shine up to 10 days. Hardens and dries any nail color. Helps get you out of the door in a flash-just 30 seconds to set. High-gloss superior shine. Double uv filters shield manicure from fading and discoloring.

title: Wrap Around Pony Synthetic Hairpiece by Jessica Simpson hairdo - R6
description: Without the hassle of trying to grow fuller hair or looking for a wig that can be worn up, Hairdo presents the Jessica Simpson ponytail: a hairpiece that's made for a full looking ponytail.  Part of Hairdo's new styleables collection, this 18" long wrap-around pony adds a long, full trend-setting pony style to any woman's hair instantly! Made with their newest Tru2Life Heat Friendly fiber Hairdo Pony hairpiece feels and styles just like your own hair!  Tru2Life  is conditioned to withstand heat up to 350 Farenheit / 160 Celsius.  Straight fibers can be curled, and curled fiber can be straightened.  Not only does these fibers style like real hair, they're light, soft, and lustrous just like real healthy hair.   With versatile styling options, now you can get the youthful flirty ponytail you've always wanted!
